snippet.title: Parse-O-Rhythm Release Date Trailer!
snippet.description:
Wishlist it on Steam here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2988830/ParseORhythm/ 

Parse-O-Rhythm, our energetic rhythm game about slashing errors, is going to be available on August 19, 2024!

This is going to be our first commercial release (on Steam) and it's been super fun working on the game so far! We can't wait for everyone to enjoy our finished project on release. This has been one of our largest projects, seconded only to Galacdrive, and it means a lot to be putting a commercial game on Steam. Thanks for playing!

-Encabulated Games
